==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Supervisor
<hw>Su`per*vis"or</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who supervises; an overseer; an inspector; a superintendent; <as>as, a
<ex>supervisor</ex> of schools</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A spectator; a looker-on.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Supervisory</ent>⟦br⟧
